Title: An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Matalahib of Quezon City to Barangay Sto. Domingo
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 687
An Act Changing the Name of Barangay Matalahib of Quezon City to Barangay Sto. Domingo
Section 1. The name of Barangay Matalahib in Quezon City is hereby changed to Barangay Sto. Domingo.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: March 7, 1984
